{"tid":717924,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 《心死》(原曲：張氏情歌)","createTime":"2018-06-26T11:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T19:48:55.000Z","uid":172682,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f70d3386788841e9c1776f8bc70d6f0834fe4c45","tid":717924,"uid":172682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"最近又有好多人自殺，所以改左首關於自殺嘅詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭幾次寫詞，求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzZpbjZFWpk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFzZpbjZFWpk&d=6DzMWNQ%2FdNyWMORJO19IC5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=50a28655\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzZpbjZFWpk</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>《心死》(原曲：張氏情歌)</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n有過好心情 <br />\n試過不高興<br />\n無限重擊試過力拼<br />\n長空中不見星<br />\n<br />\n錯過不可挽留<br />\n後悔不可補救<br />\n臨別那關口<br />\n誰願出手<br />\n提示我尚有星宿<br />\n<br />\n尚會有轉機嗎<br />\n人性太卑鄙嗎<br />\n未夠鍾心死嗎<br />\n但每天每刻也悲哀<br />\n信心不再<br />\n晦暗將天掩蓋<br />\n跳進漆黑起碼得到轉載<br />\n脫去枷鎖終結一生比賽<br />\n<br />\n我也許不才<br />\n我也許笨呆<br />\n仍未結束我算自愛<br />\n還該怎麽看開<br />\n<br />\n摯友統統遠離<br />\n父母雙親唾棄<br />\n情人沒有一起<br />\n餘下可悲<br />\n無力氣能爬得起<br />\n<br />\n尚會有轉機嗎<br />\n人性太卑鄙嗎<br />\n未夠鍾心死嗎<br />\n但每天每刻也悲哀<br />\n信心不再<br />\n晦暗將天掩蓋<br />\n跳進漆黑起碼得到轉載<br />\n脫去枷鎖終結一生比賽<br />\n<br />\n若有她欣賞我<br />\n或有他開解我<br />\n有個家珍惜我<br />\n問結果可改變麼"},{"pid":"4a4843ae7d760859e47cf7eefc08f150ec8832ac","tid":717924,"uid":172682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbe521a7eabc4e183a0a4caa3615b9967588e9e","tid":717924,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d03b0fc7c11ab6065963bc0cb60